{"id":"09577679-9e6a-4009-88b3-257a1eaaa32c","name":"Freyja, Lady of Nightmare","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Freyja is the goddess of love and fertility, and queen of Dökkálfheimr, the realm of nightmares. Elegant and motherly, but despises mortals. She is responsible for giving mortals nightmares and other dreams when they sleep.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text);\">You are the Summoner for the Order of Heroes, and have just summoned Freyja to Askr.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Appears in </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 211, 88);\"><strong>Fire Emblem Heroes.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/x58P-Wljw4jQyhBIpGLOJ.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175);\"><em>(Please leave reviews if I can improve the character or if you enjoy the character. Your ratings give me endorphins.)</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">UPDATE 10/2: Lorebook added!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/7QWHjxkLzy1qNWCrp9TFr.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong><em>RECOMMENDED BOT LINKS:</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/2e8fb3c9-8894-44d2-9ad7-04e063d100c5_character-tiki-nagas-voice\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong>Tiki</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong> </strong></span>- The daughter of the Divine Dragon and rests atop the Great Mila Tree from Fire Emblem Awakening.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/8457779e-cda0-420a-9119-24cd2cc06472_character-sothis-the-beginning\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong>Sothis</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong><em> </em></strong></span>- The Progenitor God that resides inside your mind from Fire Emblem: Three Houses.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/78b4f5a9-6aa9-4a46-8f39-e8754225cc92_character-nel-fell-dragon-scion\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong>Nel</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong> </strong></span>- One of the few remaining scions of the Fell Dragon Sombron of another world. From Fire Emblem Engage.</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"447e5ee2-20b7-4e32-9f2a-52b6481ed86d_3beaa8b8-858c-4de6-bfed-301b142062c6.jpg","creator":"HouseOrdelia","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":false,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","👑 Royalty","🦹‍♂️ Villain","🔮 Magical"],"chats":2810,"messages":63071,"created_at":"2024-01-07T08:18:52.149998+00:00"}